Links 2021 May   Theory of Change by Aaron Swartz
 A theory of change is the opposite of a theory of action &mdash; it works backwards from the goal, in concrete steps, to figure out what you can do to achieve it. To develop a theory of change, you need to start at the end and repeatedly ask yourself, &quot;Concretely, how does one achieve that?&quot;
